we all know reading is something quiet and restorative . 
it helps us to connect with ourselves and link up the outside with our inner selves . 
it is a healthy , nurturing and calming pastime . 
unlike our national sport , fights never break out in groups of readers . 
reading is educational , sustainable , non - polluting and non - violent , an A 1 activity . 
