reading , however , like many other good things in our cultural and physical environment is somewhat on the endangered list and not helped along in the least by the GST . 
canada has a very high illiteracy rate . 
one if five Canadians tested in a recent international literacy survey could not understand the label on a bottle of aspirin well enough to know the safe dosage . 
